7881:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @param  TIM_ExtTRGPrescaler The external Trigger Prescaler.
7882:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
7883:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV1: ETRP Prescaler OFF.
7884:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV2: ETRP frequency divided by 2.
